---

## 🧩 How to Play

1. Enter your **initial deposit amount**
2. Click **Start Game**
3. Select number of lines (1–3) to bet on
4. Enter bet amount per line
5. Click **Spin**
6. Watch for matching symbols and **collect your winnings!**
7. Keep playing until you run out of balance or choose to quit

---

## 💻 Running Locally

1. Clone the repository or [download ZIP](https://github.com/yourusername/slot-machine/archive/main.zip)
2. Open the project folder
3. Double-click on `index.html` to launch in your browser

> ✅ No build tools or setup required — it's pure frontend!

